            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Veneri <expan><abbr>August</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>N</abbr><ex>umerius</ex></expan> Lucius Hermeros <lb n="3"/>Aequitas <expan><abbr>mag</abbr><ex>ister</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ter</abbr><ex>tium</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Dedikant ist bereits aus CIL VI 282 (cf. p. 3004) = ILS 5615; CIL VI 283 bekannt. Zwischen 7/6 v.Chr. (magister primus) und 4/5 n.Chr. (magister iterum) erhält Hermeros das supernomen Aequitas.</p>
            </div>
